</td>
<td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:32%; padding:0in 0in 0in 0in; background-color:#e7e6e6; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top">
<p><span style="page:WordSection1"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="vertical-align:baseline"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:Palatino"><span style="color:black">Definitely/Probably benign </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:49%; padding:0in 0in 0in 0in; background-color:#e7e6e6; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top">
<p><span style="page:WordSection1"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="vertical-align:baseline"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:Palatino"><span style="color:black">Routine surveillance, consider diagnostic imaging within 6 mos </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:18%; padding:0in 0in 0in 0in; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black">
<p align="center" style="text-align:center"><span style="page:WordSection1"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="vertical-align:baseline"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:Palatino">LR-3 to LR-4</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:32%; padding:0in 0in 0in 0in; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top">
<p><span style="page:WordSection1"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="vertical-align:baseline"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:Palatino">Indeterminate/Probably HCC </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:49%; padding:0in 0in 0in 0in; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top">
<p><span style="page:WordSection1"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="vertical-align:baseline"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:Palatino">Repeat or alternative diagnostic imaging in 3-6 mos. Consider Bx for LI-RADS 4 </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:18%; padding:0in 0in 0in 0in; background-color:#e7e6e6; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black">
<p align="center" style="text-align:center"><span style="page:WordSection1"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="vertical-align:baseline"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:Palatino"><span style="color:black">LR-5</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
</td>
